telecom italia  wikipedia telecom italia from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search it has been suggested that tim brand be merged into this article discuss proposed since june  telecom italia spa type società per azioni traded as bit tit industry telecommunications founded  as stipel  as sip  as telecom italia  as tim commercial rebrand only headquarters rome italy key people arnaud de puyfontaine executive chairman flavio cattaneo ceo products fixed telephony mobile telephony broadband internet it services networking solutions digital television revenue € billion  operating income € billion  net income € billion  total assets € billion  total equity € billion  owner vivendi  number of employees  website wwwtelecomitaliacom telecom italia is an italian telecommunications company headquartered in rome which provides telephony services mobile services and dsl data services it was founded in  by the merger of several stateowned telecommunications companies the most important of which was società italiana per lesercizio telefonico pa known as sip from the earlier società idroelettrica piemontese the former state monopoly telephone operator in italy the companys stock is traded in the borsa italiana contents  history  – stipel company and early mandatory phone tax  – sip  società italiana per lesercizio telefonico  – telecom italia telecom italia mobile and dsl services  – telecom italia spa bought by telefónica   rebrand  legal problems  telecom italia mobile illegal charging money for free internet providing renewals  fraud in brazilian prepaid mobile lines  operations  sustainability  see also  references  external links historyedit – stipel company and early mandatory phone taxedit in  the phone network was reorganised by benito mussolini cabinet and stipel company was established in the same year the original core of telecom italia includes also  more different companies timo teti telve and set each of them worked in a specific geographical area it was in  that these companies merged in one single group under the name of sip – sip  società italiana per lesercizio telefonicoedit in  società idroelettrica piemontese sip a former energy company founded in  ceased producing energy and acquired all of the italian telephone companies becoming sip  società italiana per lesercizio telefonico it was run by the italian ministry of finance sip was a state monopoly from  to  and italian people had to pay the canone telecom mandatory telecom tax of about € per year plus hardware and bills in order to have a phone at home – telecom italia telecom italia mobile and dsl servicesedit telecom italia was officially created on  july  by the merger of several telecommunication companies among which sip iritel italcable telespazio and sirm this was due to a plan of reorganization of the telecommunication sector presented by iri to the minister of finance in  the mobile telephony division was spun off as tim telecom italia mobile interbusiness italy’s largest internet network was created and in the same period with tin telecom italia net and the first isps internet became a reality in italy too in  tim introduced a new prepaid rechargeable phone card gsm and one year later launched the short messaging service sms capabilityin  under the chairmanship of guido rossi telecom italia was privatised and was transformed into a large multimedia group by  the company was in debt and was bought by marco tronchetti provera the following year the group released its dsl flat service in italy alice adsl with a download speed of  kbits and an upload speed of  kbits for €month plus a monthly based tax of € the canone telecom besides the mandatory monthly bills for the home telephone numbers without a home telephone number you couldnt get the adsl service telecom italia media the groups multimedia company was formed in  from seat pagine gialle focussing its business on the television sector with la and mtv channels after the reorganization of editorial activities in  telecom italia acquired tinit and virgilio from telecom italia media the telecom italia group also operates in south america in brazil as tim brasil and in argentina and paraguay with telecom argentina group tim brasil has its local headquarters in rio de janeiro – telecom italia spa bought by telefónicaedit telecom italia had bigger debts in  and one year later ceo marco tronchetti provera resigned in  the company was bought by telco composed by telefónica and several italian banks telefónica currently owns  of telco the holding company that controls  of telecom italia in late  telefónica announced its intention to acquire the entirety of telco by january  potentially becoming telecom italias largest shareholder the plan however is being challenged by the brazilian competition authority since telefónica and telecom italia with vivo and tim respectively are the two largest telephone companies competing in brazil  rebrandedit in  telecom italia group started a rebranding process of the telephony and mobile businesses under the single tim brand in the same year the board of directors approved the new companys division the infrastrutture wireless italiane or inwit which operates  wireless towers it was revealed in october  that shareholders vivendi would raise their stakes further in the company from its current level of  as of may  vivendi owns  of the company with it ceo becoming executive chairman legal problemsedit telecom italia mobile illegal charging money for free internet providing renewalsedit telecom italia mobile illegally charged money for internet providing renew subscriptions for  years to its customers during the free subscription renewals fraud in brazilian prepaid mobile linesedit on  august  tim brasil became involved in a massive scandal in brazilian news after the release of report by the brazilian national telecommunications agency anatel the report points that on tims prepaid voice plan  market share called infinity in which the user pays roughly us for each unlimited time call the calls were intentionally dropped by the company forcing the customers to make and pay for new calls to keep talking in just one day  million calls were dropped and the total profit was approximately  million upon release of the report the public ministry of the paraná state filed a lawsuit against tim asking that it stop selling new mobile lines in brasil and pay a multimilliondollar fine for the damages against consumers operationsedit the telecom italia group provides phone landline services and mobile services in italy gsm mobile phone services in italy and brazil through its tim subsidiary tim brasil and dsl internet and telephony services in italy and san marino it also operates in international telecommunication services for other operators and corporations through its subsidiary telecom italia sparkle in  the total amount of the companys debt is about  billions € telecom italia controls also olivetti a manufacturer of computer peripherals and mobile phones on march   telecom italia leads both the direct fixed access lines market with  and the mobile “postpaid” segment with  of market share in the mobile “prepaid” segment telecom italia owns  of market share together with vodafone after the merger of wind and  italia approved on august   telecom italia is now the second country’s largest carrier with  million customers followed by vodafone  millions but it preserves its leadership on the direct fixed access lines market and the mobile “postpaid” segment telecom italia has  employees sustainabilityedit in  telecom italia subscribed to the united nations corporate responsibility initiative global compact it is also member of a number of stock market indexes which include companies focused on corporate social responsibility including the dow jones sustainability indexes and those administered by ftse groups ftsegood its partowned brazilian subsidiary tim participações is listed in the bovespas ise índice de sustentabilidade empresarial index telecom italia promotes a sustainability strategy including both environmental and social issues on june  it signed an agreement with aa to buy energy only from renewable sources see alsoedit italy portal companies portal inwit telecom italia mobile telecom italia tower naples stet referencesedit  a b c d e annual report  pdf telecom italia retrieved    telecom italia mobile spa history  economics and politics of telecommunications  telecom italia history on official site  news archive on corriereit  news archive on corriereit  the economics of mobile telecommunications page  reference   telecom italia media official site  news archive on ilsoleore  tim participações sa  pirelli as manager and investor in telecom italia   telefónica gets controlling stake in telecom italia  telecom italia group – strategic plan approved cumulative investments planned totalling around  billion euros over the three year period telecom italia retrieved    aycock jason  june  telecom italia gets ok for towers ipo values it at €b seeking alpha   lennighan mary  june  telecom italia gets regulatory ok for €bn towers ipo total telecom   exclusive vivendi moves to raise telecom italia stake to around  percent  sources reuters  october    httpswwwreuterscomarticleustelecomitaliavivendichairmaniduskbnslc  httpswwwlatecnosferacomeccocometimfregaoeuroaisuoihtml  g – tim derruba os sinais de clientes de forma proposital aponta relatório – notícias em paraná gglobocom retrieved    g – ministério público pede a suspensão de venda de chips da tim no paraná – notícias em paraná gglobocom retrieved    costanza iotti telecom patuano prepara la guerra a fossati in ballo cè uno stipendio da  milione  il fatto quotidiano il fatto quotidiano retrieved    osservatorio trimestrale sulle telecomunicazioni agcomit   the merger wind italia may unlock convergence opportunities  tlc nozze tra wind e  italia fusione da  mld per il nuovo leader del mercato mobile  sustainabil