f finding friends from the community which in turn drives usage growth and monetization  “as a global leader in the international services market we always strive to enrich our business proposition to our global customer base that’s why we have partnered with genband as they are a bestofbreed supplier of ott services for voice and mobile services” said stefano olivieri vice president line of business voice  mobile of ti sparkle “genband’s white label solution enables us to empower our customers with a fullpackage mobile application that handles voice video and instant messaging services that combined with the quality ti sparkle network services results in an unbeatable combination of flexible realtime solutions superior enduser experience and global coverage”  “we’re proud that telecom italia sparkle recognizes our ability to support a global carriergrade ott deployment” said david hiscock senior vice president of emea sales for genband “our white label solution will allow them to provide their own customers with the full range of rich communications endusers crave” key takeaways ti sparkle has selected genband’s white label ott solution to sell it as a plugplay offer to its global customer base the ott solution is based on kandy platform as a service paas deployed in the cloud kandy enables a full range of communications services including voice video and im services for end users fring differentiators extend an operator’s “coverage” beyond the physical reach of their network and reach a user over any ip network anywhere in the world a white label service that allows carriers and mvnos to launch their own brand of ott service for telephony and other communications services ease of bundling new free or premium services to existing service plans a multidevice solution that is optimized for mobile about telecom italia sparkle telecom italia sparkle spa ti sparkle is the wholly owned subsidiary of telecom italia group nyseti with the mission to develop and consolidate the italian telco’s international services business  as a leading global carrier and through a global backbone of around  km of fiber ti sparkle offers a full range of ip data cloud data center mobile data and voice solutions to fixed and mobile operators internet service providers media and content providers and to multinational enterprises its sales force is active worldwide and distributed over  countries find out more about telecom italia sparkle at tisparklecom or worldtisparklecom about genband genband a  cnbc disruptor  is a global leader in realtime communications software solutions for service providers enterprises independent software vendors systems integrators and developers in over  countries kandy its awardwinning disruptive realtime communications software development platform is built from the company’s global telecommunications network and security technologies the platform enables these companies to easily embed a full suite of voice video chat screensharing and collaboration capabilities into their existing business web and mobile applications  the company’s network modernization unified communications mobility and embedded communications solutions enable its customers to quickly capitalize on growing market segments and introduce differentiating products applications and services genband’s marketleading solutions which are deployable in the network on premise or through the cloud help its customers connect people to each other and address the growing demands of today’s consumers and businesses for realtime communications wherever they happen to be to learn more visit genbandcom genband the genband logo and icon are trademarks of genband ti sparkle media contact filippo sanpaolesi ti sparkle communication tisparklecommunicationtisparklecom              genband contacts dennis watson genband us pr      denniswatsongenbandcom catherine berthier genband international pr catherineberthiergenbandcom         contact us name  please enter your first name